  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Made by One Person :)</i></strong><br><br>Blixten Quest is a 3D Sidescroller action adventure game. <br><br>Fight fight !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/20b168bc77757f0d7904632ed06d0919.poster.avif?t=1707352689\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/20b168bc77757f0d7904632ed06d0919.webm?t=1707352689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/20b168bc77757f0d7904632ed06d0919.mp4?t=1707352689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/69d1ac3efe8fca41d3a2149403cc0eb7.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Adventure is the key! Explore, Level up, talking with people, find new places like Forest,Winter,Desert,Caves,Castle and moreee!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/cfd3d8d246c88379e78181c65cbb188f.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Hack and Slash feeling, kills so many you want and use your different abilites. Switch Weapons and your class change. Use Spells,Melee and Range attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/563916ad2c44c7495636b09a4857e0ba.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Find loots like, Weapons,Armors,Rings,Backs and much more ! Remember there is Common, Uncommon, Rare and Epic and maybe more?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/68155f7241adea5e65bd4fb09a7a551a.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>There is challange, fight Bosses, enemies (Normal and Elite).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/17296a29050d6f0467c366569f30f908.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Gathering and Crafting is something you need to do. Find Stones, Woods and herbs.<br><br><strong>Other Features & Is Coming</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Achivement.<br></li><li>Rift<br></li><li>Events<br></li><li>And more is coming!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><i>Made by One Person :)</i></strong><br><br>Blixten Quest is a 3D Sidescroller action adventure game. <br><br>Fight fight !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/20b168bc77757f0d7904632ed06d0919.poster.avif?t=1707352689\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/20b168bc77757f0d7904632ed06d0919.webm?t=1707352689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/20b168bc77757f0d7904632ed06d0919.mp4?t=1707352689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/69d1ac3efe8fca41d3a2149403cc0eb7.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Adventure is the key! Explore, Level up, talking with people, find new places like Forest,Winter,Desert,Caves,Castle and moreee!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/cfd3d8d246c88379e78181c65cbb188f.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Hack and Slash feeling, kills so many you want and use your different abilites. Switch Weapons and your class change. Use Spells,Melee and Range attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/563916ad2c44c7495636b09a4857e0ba.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Find loots like, Weapons,Armors,Rings,Backs and much more ! Remember there is Common, Uncommon, Rare and Epic and maybe more?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/68155f7241adea5e65bd4fb09a7a551a.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>There is challange, fight Bosses, enemies (Normal and Elite).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922560/extras/17296a29050d6f0467c366569f30f908.avif?t=1707352689\" width=800 height=142 /></span><br>Gathering and Crafting is something you need to do. Find Stones, Woods and herbs.<br><br><strong>Other Features & Is Coming</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Achivement.<br></li><li>Rift<br></li><li>Events<br></li><li>And more is coming!</li></ul>",
